    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade find that looks and feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or chip. Inside, the interior is pristine; the leather remains soft and supple, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound with a complete service history, ensuring it drives as beautifully as it looks. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example of this model.",
