    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, so it\u2019s still looking great and running smoothly. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go! Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how nicely it handles. Can't wait to find it a great new home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a quintessential driver\u2019s machine powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring torsional rigidity during spirited cornering. Recent mechanical service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. It sits on staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in high-performance radial tires, offering precise turn-in and exceptional mechanical grip. A mechanically sorted, analog performance icon ready for the canyon roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
